
Use on portable media
=====================

Distributions of SlingshotSMS do not require installation of 
dependency or installation at all. They can be run from removable media, like
USB sticks.

The installation of drivers for GSM modems is required, though, especially for 
modems which connect via USB. For those using MultiModems, the drivers are 
`available online <http://www.multitech.com/en_US/SUPPORT/Families/multimodemgprs/drivers.asp>`_

Download SlingshotSMS.zip from GitHub, unzip onto USB stick
Plug in USB stick, click on mac/ or windows/ depending on your system.

Windows
-------

Double-click on SlingshotSMS.exe

Mac
---

Double-click on SlingshotSMS.command
